room_title: Escape room "Reactor Meltdown" by GetOut Games in Salt Lake City
room_address: 202 W 400 S Salt Lake City, UT 84101
room_description: SLC’s nuclear experiment has gone awry. The reactor’s core temperature is rising and coolant is leaking throughout the plant. Your team’s mission is simple: shut down the reactor before it melts down. You’ll have 60 minutes to solve the cryptic clues left behind by the plant’s main scientist and prevent a nuclear disaster.
